{"tid":548047,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【接二連三】iPhone 電池又爆炸　香港 IFC Apple Store 兩員工送院","createTime":"2018-02-02T06:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T18:46:49.000Z","uid":8171,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"77029152249a9096d333b384437fb0c6fb2b83c1","tid":548047,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"最近在 Apple Store 不斷發生電池爆炸事故，繼瑞士、西班牙之後，香港的 Apple Store 也中招。<br />\n<br />\n香港 IFC 的 Apple Store 在中午發生 iPhone 電池爆炸事故，兩名蘋果男員工在維修 iPhone 電池的時候，電池突然冒煙，警方和消防員很快到達現場，並將不適的兩名蘋果男員工送院，目前未知道肇事 iPhone 型號。<br />\n<br />\n早前在瑞士、西班牙的 Apple Store，員工們維修 iPhone 電池的時候會發生類似電池冒煙爆炸事件，結果弄得 Apple Store 緊急疏散，事件令人懷疑蘋果過保 iPhone 換電減價是否令大量早已老化的電池送到 Apple Store，引發多宗 Apple Store 電池爆炸事故。不過，由於未知今次在香港出事的 iPhone 型號，故無法確定事件的原因。"},{"pid":"b2398ad74f296e9ed0b57e23bd3f71c5ba865e6e","tid":548047,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e994bfc0847a7f3b4ac7d6be7cc159ac960b3e5","tid":548047,"uid":60655,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"ifandog不願面對事實"},{"pid":"463cca4cc9b71332c707c2a7ff2ef62e08dc34c7","tid":548047,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"影衰Apple 炒得"},{"pid":"d0fb8ca60e6f1d793b1c8bbddb58ed65d0a9883c","tid":548047,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"係咪將貨就價, 用埋的checp雞電換"},{"pid":"3051d19a27a421820c2da8bfe633693f8a721a0a","tid":548047,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"一早出可換電就唔會咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7cdc4d77e03c21fbb0cb268b19281a16c68007","tid":548047,"uid":81397,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:45:45.000Z","msg":"第三個post已經變成爆炸<img src=\"/assets/fac